# magic-link login — quick internal sketch. Styled, but casual: house style on,
# only the obvious nodes classed (the rest fall back to plain), no governance.
...@../../../references/style

user: User           { class: actor }
app:  Web App        { class: svc }
api:  Auth API       { class: svc }
mail: Email                            # left unclassed — falls back to plain box
db:   Token Store    { class: store }

user -> app: enter email
app -> api: request link
api -> db: store token
api -> mail: send link
user -> app: click link
app -> api: verify token
api -> db: check + consume
api -> app: issue session
